<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idb55b7d65-47c4-11f1-9665-b3e99855dc0d" identifier="/us/usc/t6/s763"><num value="763">§ 763.</num><heading> Transfer of Noble Training Center</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Noble Training Center is transferred to the Center for Domestic Preparedness. The Center for Domestic Preparedness shall integrate the Noble Training Center into the program structure of the Center for Domestic Preparedness.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idb55b7d66-47c4-11f1-9665-b3e99855dc0d">(<ref href="/us/pl/109/295/tVI/s663">Pub. L. 109–295, title VI, § 663</ref>, <date date="2006-10-04">Oct. 4, 2006</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/120/1433">120 Stat. 1433</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
